STYLESHEET.CSS
#nav{
background-color: darkgreen;
height: 35px;
font-size: 25px;
font-weight: bold;
font: Tahoma;
}

#nav ul{
padding: 0;
margin: 0;
list-style-type: none;
text-align: center;
}

#nav li{
display: inline;                       /*make the text side by side (HORIZONTAL)*/
padding: 15px;
vertical-align: middle;
}

#nav a{
text-decoration: none;
padding: 8px;
color: white;
vertical-align: middle;
}

#nav a:hover{
color: black;
background-color: white;
}



Notes:
Use the <div> elements to make a section.
"text-decoration" is not inheritable, so that we need to put it in a{}.
